SIMPLE: millionth
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Millionth
<hw>Mil"lionth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Being the last one
of a million of units or objects counted in regular order from the first
of a series or succession; being one of a million.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Millionth</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Millionth
<hw>Mil"lionth</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quotient of a unit divided
by one million; one of a million equal parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Milliped</ent>⟦br⟧
